{"tid":2218984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］介紹一本連平野鈴子都推介嘅網絡刊物...","createTime":"2020-09-26T14:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T19:36:18.000Z","uid":234894,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4d1a8c449d2504a89cd499bbe70d282e6f80f762","tid":2218984,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdZQxrh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdZQxrh.jpg&h=10fb372f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢本叫做《自由港》嘅網絡刊物係由一班海外手足負責營運，九月先至啱啱出第一期，中英雙語，內容其實都好豐富，有海外戰線嘅訪問，亦都有唔同方面嘅論述。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdmfJx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdmfJx4.jpg&h=8aba8829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平野鈴子早兩日都推薦過呢本野<br />\n<br />\n而且呢本野啱啱出咗唔夠一個月就比五毛搞，一星期之內俾人瘋狂舉報，Facebook同埋Twitter都曾經因為大量舉報俾人封鎖，Twitter至今仍未解封<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ktf0UE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtf0UE3.jpg&h=0e0db3f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7uy55M3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7uy55M3.jpg&h=76e530b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果睇過小弟嘅出Post記錄,都應該知道唔係第一次推介呢本嘢，其實佢哋嘅營運團隊的確係有心機，就算因為唔同原因要離開香港，都希望能夠繼續喺唔同崗位上出一分力，所以希望各位巴打如果可以嘅入去俾個like俾個share，當係支持下佢哋。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HarbourofFreedomHongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHarbourofFreedomHongKong%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=132bb297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HarbourofFreedomHongKong/</a><br />\nInstagram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/harbouroffreedom?igshid=1jgpw3iutce3t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fharbouroffreedom%3Figshid%3D1jgpw3iutce3t&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=e9842b9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/harbouroffreedom?igshid=1jgpw3iutce3t</a><br />\nTelegram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HarbourofFreedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHarbourofFreedom&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=fc8b9ed0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HarbourofFreedom</a>"},{"pid":"8aad8ab57e292fd8bfbd5b470d42ffb9eea7e454","tid":2218984,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c477da0de1de5ac1741fd2bb7aaff6803164e1","tid":2218984,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c28c046df3c4b90408ee56c3783e70eb3cbaf3d","tid":2218984,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cd34e7c20294620b7684a78fab144c46683ad1","tid":2218984,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637231c5af08bd11a0b6fc636be6df7912d670c7","tid":2218984,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278a3eb92f6072065e416667150e3